net.casper.data.model

Class CRowMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.casper.data.model.CRowMetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, ResultSetMetaData, Wrapper

    public class CRowMetaData
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable, ResultSetMetaData
    Contains meta-data / configuration information for a "table" or "rowset" in cdataset. This includes the column names types, and mappings between the two associations Also contains primary key configuration for the dataset.

    Because the current interface implements the ResultSetMetaData interface, it should be compatible, for the most part, with a sufficient set of core JDBC functionality. Requires Java 1.4 (or later).
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    $Revision: 111 $
    Author:
